    Scope and Contents
The Board of Regents Regulations File consists of copies of administrative regulations issued in notebook form, memoranda, users guide, index and superseded pages.  Regulation subjects include: Board Committees,  Freedom of Information Act,  Programs and their approval, Long-range planning, faculty and administrative appointments, and financial affairs.  Superseded pages have been kept for the Regulations notebook.  Memoranda are from the Secretary of the Board of Regents to Board members and NIU Controller.  Memoranda also includes a Sick Leave Benefits Summary from SSU Personnel Director to the university community.  The user's Guide and Index includes Governance policies and the Regency Universities Act.

These files are arranged according to the sections of the Board of Regents Manual.  
  
